Awesome neighborhood spot. Super friendly folks running this place that always dole out generous portions. Jerk chicken is always perfectly spicy and flavorful and oxtail is fall off the bone tender. They’ll also make combos if you ask (for a couple extra bucks). I usually get jerk chicken and oxtail combo. Ask for the homemade hot sauce on the side if you like spicy.

This is an Amazingly Clean, Professional, Courteous and Pleasantly Delicious "Taste of Jamaica" I've experienced in a Very, Very long time!! The Food was absolutely Fabulous!!! Pull right off the bone!! The Atmosphere was also very lively, friendly, as the reggae music filtered throughout! Trust me! If you like jamaican food, anything from  Oxtails,Jerk Chicken,  Red Snapper, Curry Chicken  etc.....

I found this restaurant on Uber eats. I have ordered from them about 5 or 6 times. It probably could have been more times but I have lost track due to cancellations on their end...They have GREAT oxtail and great food but it seems like every other order it has to be canceled because they seem to conveniently run out of food every time. There is never any patties or oxtails or if they don’t have an item, instead of calling the customer to let them know, they substitute the item missing for something I didn’t ask for. I have tried to bear with them, but it seems to be happening way too much. I had to unmark it as a favorite. The food is great, but ya’ll gotta stay prepared and stop conveniently running out of food. I will not be ordering from here anymore.

Leaving no star wasn't an option.  I ordered a large curry goat dinner with jerk gravy over my pigeon peas and rice for delivery with CoCo bread and plantains. I get a call saying they have no more cabbage or CoCo bread. Offered me some extra plantains I said no, I asked for a Champagne cola he says I'll send 2, I get my food there is all fat and bones on some dry goat. The plantains were dry and no gravy on my rice. 1 Champagne cola  and 1 cream soda. I will never order from this place again. Still waiting on Ashton Kutcher to jump out on me. $25 down the drain.

As a health and beauty specialists...I recognize these guys are better than any carry out you can think of. Whether it be Chinese, McDonalds, Popeyes, Wendy’s, Any Fried Food places, etc. As Americans continue to eat out waaay more than they cook, it becomes ever more important to be conscious of what your putting in your vehicular human body. Goat has not been tainted like chicken and beef in America. And there aren’t too many places to get tasty healthy meat such as goat which has a great amount of protein and low in fat. The Cabbage contains lots of fiber and nutrients essential to living a healthy lifestyle. And the tasty plantains contains so many minerals needed for your body to function properly. American food places are death beds. This place is great place to eat live. Feel free to do your own personal research. Peace.
